## ❌ Remaining Screens (Not Yet Implemented)

### Phase 1: Onboarding Flow (4 screens)
> These form a sequential first-time-user experience after login.

| # | Design File | Screen Name | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | [the_awakening_screen.png](file:///c:/Users/aayan/OneDrive/Desktop/study/screen/the_awakening_screen.png) | **The Awakening** | System initialization — player name, target CGPA slider, semester picker, "Begin Journey" CTA |
| 2 | [quest_line_initialization_screen.png](file:///c:/Users/aayan/OneDrive/Desktop/study/screen/quest_line_initialization_screen.png) | **Quest Line Initialization** | Select engineering branch, pick semester subjects with icons, paginated (step 2 of 4) |
| 3 | [goal_alignment_screen.png](file:///c:/Users/aayan/OneDrive/Desktop/study/screen/goal_alignment_screen.png) | **Goal Alignment** | CGPA target slider, primary semester focus (Exam Performance / Skill Mastery / Consistency), step 3 of 4 |
| 4 | [final_calibration_screen.png](file:///c:/Users/aayan/OneDrive/Desktop/study/screen/final_calibration_screen.png) | **Final Calibration** | Summary review — master name, zen branch, core target; hero image; "Enter the Dojo" CTA |

#### Implementation Notes
- Create `src/screens/onboarding/` folder with 4 screens
- Add an `OnboardingContext` to persist selected values across steps
- Store onboarding data in Supabase `players` table
- Add a `has_completed_onboarding` flag to skip flow on subsequent logins
- Wire into [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/aayan/OneDrive/Desktop/study/4th-sem-weapon/App.tsx) navigation: after `SignedIn`, check onboarding status → show onboarding flow OR main tabs

