## 📊 Overall Progress

```
Built:      ██████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  9/23 screens  (39%)
Remaining:  ░░░░░░░░░░██████████████░  14/23 screens (61%)
```

## Suggested Implementation Priority

1. **🔴 Phase 1 — Onboarding** (Critical: first-time user experience is currently missing)
2. **🟡 Phase 2 — Enhance Existing Screens** (Quick wins: improve already-built screens)
3. **🟢 Phase 3 — PYQ Vault** (Major new feature area)
4. **🔵 Phase 4 — AI Strategy** (Advanced AI features)
5. **⚪ Phase 5 — Modals** (Polish & supporting screens)

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- After each screen is built, run the app with `npx expo start` and visually compare against the design PNG
- Test the full onboarding flow end-to-end after Phase 1
- Test navigation between all screens after each phase

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The onboarding flow (Phase 1) is the most critical missing piece — without it, new users land directly on the dashboard with no context. This should be the first priority.
